Class ElementRouter<T extends ElementBase>

java.lang.Object
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.http_server.routes.SoileRouter
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.http_server.routes.ElementRouter<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The base for this Element Router (i.e. the ElementBase the router is targeting)
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProjectRouter, TaskRouter
public class ElementRouter<T extends ElementBase> extends SoileRouter
Generic router for all different types of Elements. Descriptions for the individual calls can be obtained from the API document ( method names are 1:1 reflected by operation Names)
Author:
Thomas Pfau
